{
  "id": "6a3da276f100b17a26efaf36",
  "title": "takkerのサブスク棚卸し",
  "created": 1782424183,
  "updated": 1782455116,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a3da276f100b17a26efaf36",
      "text": "takkerのサブスク棚卸し",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782424183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a83",
      "text": "[Claude Code Max 5x]を捻出できるかやってみる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782424201
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de81300000000007c3656",
      "text": " 外せないもの",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441970,
      "updated": 1782441973
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a84",
      "text": "  生命保険：わからん",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782441978
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a85",
      "text": "  損害保険：わからん",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782441978
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a86",
      "text": "  電気：わからん",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782441978
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a87",
      "text": "  ガス：わからん",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782441978
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a88",
      "text": "  水道：わからん",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782441978
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a89",
      "text": "  食費：わからん",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782441978
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a8a",
      "text": "  医療費：わからん",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782441978
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de81f00000000007c3666",
      "text": "  授業料：535800円/年",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441982,
      "updated": 1782441982
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de81f00000000007c3667",
      "text": "  　解約できません",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441982,
      "updated": 1782441982
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de81f00000000007c3668",
      "text": "  　[Claude Code Max 5x]を年額換算すると$1200/年≒192000円/年",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441982,
      "updated": 1782441982
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de81f00000000007c3669",
      "text": "  　授業料の1/3くらい払うことになるのか、やばいな",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441982,
      "updated": 1782441982
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de81f00000000007c366a",
      "text": "  　「大学院=[Claude Code Max 5x]+[Claude Code Max 20x]」くらいの価値計算か",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441982,
      "updated": 1782441982
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de81f00000000007c366b",
      "text": "  　iPhone Proもこのくらいか",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441982,
      "updated": 1782441982
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de81f00000000007c366c",
      "text": "  　 iPhone Pro1台でClaude Codeを召喚できると考えれば安いのかもしれない",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441982,
      "updated": 1782441982
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de82200000000007c3671",
      "text": "  通学定期：たぶん70000円/年",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441985,
      "updated": 1782441985
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de82200000000007c3672",
      "text": "  　これは仕方ない",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441985,
      "updated": 1782441985
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de82900000000007c3676",
      "text": "  [Gyazo Pro]：5880円/年",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441992,
      "updated": 1782441992
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de85a00000000007c3683",
      "text": "  [ココヘリ]：6600円/年",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782442041,
      "updated": 1782442041
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de86c00000000007c3689",
      "text": "   登山に必須",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782442059,
      "updated": 1782442063
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de81800000000007c3657",
      "text": " それ以外",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441975,
      "updated": 1782441976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a8b",
      "text": "  [basefood]：最近延期している",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782442000
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a8c",
      "text": "  　だいたい4500円/月？",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782442000
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a8d",
      "text": "  [TTFC]：960円/月",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782442001
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a8e",
      "text": "   よく延期している",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782442001
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a8f",
      "text": "   残念ながら1年以上見てない",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782442001
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a90",
      "text": "   　一旦解約してもいいかも",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782442001
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de79900000000007c3650",
      "text": "  体育館の年パス：10000円/年",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441848,
      "updated": 1782442003
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de7a700000000007c3651",
      "text": "   脚折れちゃったのでしばらく行けなくなっちゃった",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441862,
      "updated": 1782442003
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de7af00000000007c3652",
      "text": "   まあ元取れるくらいもう通ってるはずなのでいいだろう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441870,
      "updated": 1782442003
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de7ba00000000007c3653",
      "text": "   骨がくっついたらまた買おう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441881,
      "updated": 1782442003
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de86100000000007c3688",
      "text": " [OpenCode Go]：$10/月",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782442050,
      "updated": 1782442053
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3df40500000000004cda4e",
      "text": "  た　り　な　い",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782445028,
      "updated": 1782445031
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a95",
      "text": " [Google AI Pro]：2900円/月",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782424183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a96",
      "text": "  まだ無料期間中",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782424183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a97",
      "text": "  9月から課金される",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782424183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3ddfbe000000000095311f",
      "text": "   これおなじ 嫌だ[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1782439871,
      "updated": 1782439903
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de82f0000000000953124",
      "text": "    しかしオマケでgoogleのクラウドストレージがもらえるのが安心感あってやめづらい",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1782442032,
      "updated": 1782442069
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de87e00000000007c368a",
      "text": "    とはいえ5TBも要らないきもち[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782442083,
      "updated": 1782442084
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de88500000000007c368b",
      "text": "     2TBあれば十分",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782442085,
      "updated": 1782442088
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de83a00000000007c367b",
      "text": "   [Google AI Plus]でもいいかなあ[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782442009,
      "updated": 1782442018
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de84300000000007c367c",
      "text": "    DeepResearchを今後多用するようになったらProに切り上げればいい？",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782442018,
      "updated": 1782442033
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de8580000000000953125",
      "text": "    プランおおくてわけわかめ[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1782442072,
      "updated": 1782442078
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3ded420000000000b4f04a",
      "text": "    同じく[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1782443331,
      "updated": 1782443356
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3ded5b0000000000b4f04b",
      "text": "    \t[比較表を作ってくれてる人 https://nomolk.hatenablog.com/entry/2026/04/07/211801]のページを度々見返すが、それでもなんだかよくわからん",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1782443356,
      "updated": 1782443363
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a98",
      "text": " [YAMAPプレミアム]：5700円/年",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782424183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a9a",
      "text": " [日経電子版]：4277円/月",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782424183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dda9b0000000000bc2b73",
      "text": "  楽天証券かなんかでついてくるんだっけ[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1782438556,
      "updated": 1782438564
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3ddac20000000000bc2b74",
      "text": "   日経テレコンだけだった",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1782438595,
      "updated": 1782438597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de7cc00000000007c3654",
      "text": "   日経テレコンは今の大学だとタダで使えるからそっちでもいい[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441899,
      "updated": 1782441911
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a9b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782424183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a9c",
      "text": "解約できるのそんなになかった[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782424183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a9d",
      "text": " ココヘリとYAMAPは必須だし",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782424183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a9e",
      "text": " [TTFC]解約すれば、[Claude Code Pro]くらいは捻出できそうだけど、聞いた感じ[OpenCode Go]から乗り換えるほどの魅力はなさそう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782424183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134a9f",
      "text": " AI系が[Google AI Pro]と[OpenCode Go]とで被っているけど、[Google AI Pro]ではCoding Agentの特典ほぼないから仕方ないか……",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782424183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3da2970000000000134aa0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782424183,
      "updated": 1782424183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd62d0000000000af4cb4",
      "text": "[サブスク棚卸しの感想]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782437422,
      "updated": 1782437428
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd63c0000000000af4cb5",
      "text": " [sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782437436,
      "updated": 1782437446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd47100000000000a33f6",
      "text": "  リッチな社会人でなければ、熱心な趣味に月1～2万かけれるかって感じかなぁ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782436978,
      "updated": 1782437446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd56a0000000000af4cab",
      "text": "  \t「熱心な趣味」として何を据えるか……",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782437227,
      "updated": 1782437446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd48200000000000a33f8",
      "text": "   \t[takker.icon]さんは登山（ココヘリとYAMAP）にかけている",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782436995,
      "updated": 1782437446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de74b00000000007c364a",
      "text": "   \t 少なくともココヘリは安全面から外せない[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441770,
      "updated": 1782441784
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd49000000000000a33f9",
      "text": "   \t[sta.icon]は生成AI、Claudeにかけている（MAX x5）",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782437009,
      "updated": 1782437446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd5460000000000af4ca7",
      "text": "   \t\t過去はマンガやラノベだったこともある",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782437192,
      "updated": 1782437446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd49b00000000000a33fa",
      "text": "   \t他には美容院など美容に月1～2万かけてる人や、地方住で毎週都会に出てる（交通費片道1000円以上かかる）人とかもいる etc",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782437020,
      "updated": 1782437446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd64f0000000000af4cb6",
      "text": "   二つは選べない",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782437457,
      "updated": 1782437459
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd59e0000000000af4cad",
      "text": " \tあとはどれだけ自分に厳しくして、少しでも減らせるか……",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782437279,
      "updated": 1782437446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd5a80000000000af4cae",
      "text": "  \t[takker.icon]さんの上記のを見ると、[sta.icon]だったら以下を考えてみるかなぁ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782437289,
      "updated": 1782437446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd5b50000000000af4caf",
      "text": "  \t\t日経電子版。ネットのニュースで済ませられないか？",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782437302,
      "updated": 1782437446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de75c00000000007c364b",
      "text": "  \t\t　これ親が課金しているから別に関係なかったりする[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441787,
      "updated": 1782441798
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd5c40000000000af4cb0",
      "text": "  \t\tGyazo Pro。コセンスメインなら要らない可能性がある",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782437317,
      "updated": 1782437446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de76800000000007c364c",
      "text": "  \t\t OCR多用しているので必須[takker.icon*3]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441799,
      "updated": 1782442374
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de9ae00000000007c3690",
      "text": "  \t\t 検索もかなり使う",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782442381,
      "updated": 1782442388
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd5d00000000000af4cb1",
      "text": "  \t\tTTFC。直近見てないならいったん捨ててみても良さそう",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782437329,
      "updated": 1782437446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de77200000000007c364d",
      "text": "  \t\t これは解約したい[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441809,
      "updated": 1782441812
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd5db0000000000af4cb2",
      "text": "  \tただ、こればっかり当人でないとわからない",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782437340,
      "updated": 1782437446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3dd5fa0000000000af4cb3",
      "text": "  \t\t極論僕は「セルフバリカンで坊主にすれば美容院代はゼロ円」「なんでみんなやらないんだろ」「もったいな」と思っているが、そんな単純ではない",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782437371,
      "updated": 1782437446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de9bc00000000007c3691",
      "text": "  \t\tそもそも髪切るのよく忘れるので実質美容院代ゼロ()[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782442395,
      "updated": 1782442412
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3ddae60000000000bc2b75",
      "text": " 山への課金が多くていい[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1782438630,
      "updated": 1782438641
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3ddae70000000000bc2b76",
      "text": "  ✌️[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782438632,
      "updated": 1782441957
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3de7e500000000007c3655",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782441925,
      "updated": 1782441925
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e16460000000000d6c9de",
      "text": "[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782453830,
      "updated": 1782453831
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e16470000000000d6c9e0",
      "text": "\t参考になるかどうかは分かりませんが、私はサブスクをこんな感じで管理してます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782453831,
      "updated": 1782454235
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e16f900000000009a90d8",
      "text": "\t\tサブスクは一ヶ月に一回ぐらいのペースで見直していて",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782454009,
      "updated": 1782454491
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e170e00000000009a90d9",
      "text": " \t\t1. 月額と年額ではいくら掛かってるか",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782454031,
      "updated": 1782454496
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e171700000000009a90da",
      "text": " \t\t2. 今新しくサブスクを足すとどうなるか",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782454039,
      "updated": 1782454496
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e172300000000009a90db",
      "text": " \t\t3. 今使ってない無駄になっているサブスクはあるか",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782454052,
      "updated": 1782454496
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e174b00000000009a90dc",
      "text": "\t\tみたいな観点からサービスを足したり引いたりしてます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782454092,
      "updated": 1782454497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e19fb00000000009a90e7",
      "text": "\t\tあと表にして何にいくら掛かっているかを可視化すると管理しやすくなるのでおすすめです",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782454779,
      "updated": 1782454796
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e16940000000000d6c9e2",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/b19d089eb0da8e43fdaad531a8ba9650]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782453909,
      "updated": 1782454498
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e18e600000000009a90de",
      "text": "\t\t生活費に関しては家計簿アプリを使っていて、別枠管理です",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782454502,
      "updated": 1782455029
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e18fd00000000009a90df",
      "text": "\t\t\t[nyarla.icon]は実家暮らしなので大した額を管理している訳ではないですが、一応預貯金の状態はパッと見で把握してます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782454526,
      "updated": 1782454595
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e1afa00000000009a90e8",
      "text": "\t\t\tあと現金の管理はしていなくて、 主にカード払いの額とカードの残債、預金残高を管理していますね",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782455034,
      "updated": 1782455116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e196d00000000009a90e0",
      "text": "\t\tちなみに↑は nocodb という Web アプリケーションを VPS へデプロイして使ってます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782454637,
      "updated": 1782454826
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e196f00000000009a90e1",
      "text": "\t\t\tとは言え、表を作ること自体は Google スプレッドシートでも出来そう",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782454639,
      "updated": 1782454642
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e16470000000000d6c9df",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1782453831,
      "updated": 1782453831
    }
  ]
}